This is a remake of the map gg_square_v2 by xwojski69x

I decided to release this remake with improvements due to the map layout being great and one of my personal favourites.

It has 40 spawn points now (20 T, 20 CT) so enough for any server.

Credits go to:

Custom Nav File by Chizbone

BoHaRoX for the lego textures

Karatekaefer for the great custom skybox

MoHaX_cm for the palmtree prefab
